Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sir Trillram.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Landing Castle is about\Nto take its meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so this laser transmission\Nwill be terminated soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wrap this up quickly, shall we?\NWhat is the status of our rat extermination?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are we awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no you don't.\NYou need to stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The school. The enemy hasn't\Nfigured out we're here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to give them\Nthe slip for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho and his friends,\Nyou mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say they're\Ngoing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Using the equipment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Against that Martian Kataphrakt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the deal with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from HQ, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the citizens are evacuated, we're\Nto abandon this base and pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have someone still\Nfighting out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Koichiro Marito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darzana Magbaredge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the amphibious assault ship\NWadatsumi, 4th Fleet Escort Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaoru Mizusaki, my XO.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One of our people is still fighting\Nin the northern district!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason we're still secure here\Nis because she's holding them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"She"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Yuki Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A radio jamming field is covering\Nthe entire Shinawara area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPS is down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we went out to rescue her, we wouldn't\Nbe able to pinpoint her location data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our responsibility is to escort and protect\Nthe ferries that are carrying refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are still people who\Nhaven't made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My kids' names weren't on\Nthe passenger manifest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll put in a request\Nto HQ to form a rescue party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you one\Nlanding craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you can't put together\Nenough people to crew her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I expect you\Nto let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao? You're here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that,\Nthat's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what you kids\Nare getting yourselves into?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly aware\Nthat it's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, that Martian is\Nobsessed with trying to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, as long as\Nwe stick to the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,his attacks won't spread to the\Ncity proper or the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, everyone who lives\Naround here has been evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, that doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okisuke is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Make decisions as circumstances dictate. If you\Nhave to, trust your gut and make the call."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you\Nalways tell me, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that this\Nis one of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let an injured\Nperson do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you\Nto keep them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to cheer up and reassure\Nthe people who are scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's something\Nthat we just can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess... You wished for peace\Nmore than anyone, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who would do such a thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what you are saying is that not\Nonly did you fail to kill the rat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you have even lost track of where\Nit may have gone to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect,\NMilord Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She has not eluded me just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From that tunnel she fled into,\Nshe could only go to one area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, Shinawara's\Nnorthern district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When she grows impatient and pokes\Nher head out of her hidey-hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my Nilokeras' vaunted eagle eyes\Nwill immediately spot him, and-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we have the luxury\Nof playing the waiting game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we do not have the rat's\Nexact location, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shall simply blow the entire\Ncity to kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shall conduct a\Nmeteor bombardment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-Milord Saazbaum! Count Cruhteo's\NLanding Castle is too close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would he not view that\Nas an attack against him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when sacrifices\Nmust be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Orbital corrections\Nwill take several hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To ensure that the rat does not\Nflee elsewhere in the meantime,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}maintain a close watch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been collecting all we know\Nabout that Martian Kataphrakt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bullets you fired at it didn't bounce off,\Nthey were all absorbed, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Borderline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such impudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:07:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just bullets. When active sensor\Npings hit it, they don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Infrared, acoustic detection, lasers,\Nthey're all useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was no echo return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't just absorb kinetic energy,\Nbut also radio waves and lasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the special\Ncharacteristic of that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The energy field\Nthat covers its surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call it a barrier, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier that absorbs\Nanything that touches it:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matter, light, sound,\Nradio waves, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, how can he see\Nwhat's on our side of the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All information from the outside\Nis blocked by the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that he can't see or hear anything\Non this side through the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.33,Egg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier\N\NAbsorb
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my opinion, the inside surface of that\Nbarrier appears completely black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.47,Block,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.34,Block,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light\NSound
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.33,Block,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light\NSound\NRadio Waves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's true,\Nwhy do his attacks hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. How can he hit\Nanything if he's not looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He precisely targeted us from the other side\Nof a building when we were running from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then, even though he'd been\Nchasing us so relentlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he gave up the chase the instant\Nwe ran into the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that he wasn't the one who was looking\Nat what was outside the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that he's using some separate cameras\Nto allow him to see, probably in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he kept managing to\Ntrack us no matter how far we ran,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and why he didn't want\Nto go into the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he can't see what's in front\Nof him when that barrier is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably searching for us\Nfrom overhead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And conversely, it means we're safe as long\Nas we stay under cover like we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the instant we go out,\Nhe'll spot us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably only get\None chance at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, we're out of\Nbackup batteries...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And whose turn was it to check\Nthem this week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frigging Marito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Inaho..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be us three\Nheading out in the Kats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we need two more people\Nfor the decoy truck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do we ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princ-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Scandanavian babe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that it is my duty to go through\Nthis time of crisis, this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Middle schooler syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He killed my father.\NLet me take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our own lives will\Nbe on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.\NYou can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We carry out the plan tomorrow morning.\NWe leave at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to drive off\Nthat Martian Kataphrakt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Inko?\NCan't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The student council office\Nis pretty cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the heat is turned off. We want to\Nminimize any signs of human habitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm is sleeping like\Na baby, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he doesn't\Ncatch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're worried\Nabout a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you guys\Nmight die tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm fearless\Nor anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going\Nto be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then they were all...\NLike they were nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens to us, we probably\Nwon't even know what hit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of regrets will\NI have in that moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to just sit around doing\Nnothing as I think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I feel.\NCalm probably does, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not\Nup for it, Inko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.\NI'll go rest up for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho. Don't catch a cold, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We five will now\Ncarry out the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to rescue friendly forces and civilians still\Nremaining in Shinawara's northern district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make that we six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Magbaredge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've delegated our ferry\Nescort duties to XO Mizusaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're to rendezvous with us\Nafter the op is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken an interest in you,\NLt. Koichiro Marito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A signal round...\NThree reds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's in the direction\Nof the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Commencing attack"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, rat...\NTime to finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving out!\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\NThis road's so narrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry about it! You won't\Nhave points deducted today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see it! 10 o'clock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, pillbug!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commence operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...\NIt can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's stopped moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Inaho said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Release the safety.\NRaise it. Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simple, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stinking rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Kaizuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Marito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Trillram!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this wasn't\Npart of the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The trailer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Milord?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me its position!\NWhere is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-To your southwest,\Nheading towards the city center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is crazy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cover me! That bat's wake\Nis dispersing the smoke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have to shoot it down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Calm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terran Kataphrakts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. My stabilizer's gone,\Nbut I can still run, barely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rockets seem to work fine\Non that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A sky carrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Vers tactical transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm given to understand that it has\Nno special equipment or capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,beyond machine guns\Nand missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voltage, check.\NOil pressure, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Temperature, check.\NRPMs, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.05,Barrier,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}Nao, \NGood luck!\N -Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Force feedback\Nchecking program, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ejection seat functional.\NIFF confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tactical datalink, activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All systems green.\NHold open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1200 meters to destination. Estimated time\Nto rendezvous, 93 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy some time.\NBe quiet for a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You dare mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've led me\Non quite the chase...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run, it's me he's after!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will not. It is 54 seconds until\Nour estimated rendezvous time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall buy us that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How pathetic... You are going\Nto beg for your lives?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Restrain yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Vers Princess Royal, I shall\Nnot tolerate this outrageous behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness Asseylum\NVers Allusia? It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave at once, you ill-mannered ruffian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire all missiles!\NTarget: enemy Martian Kataphrakt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master arm switch. Fire control.\NLower dampers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inko, hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You waste your time! My Nilokeras'\Ndefenses are impregnable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The likes of you\Ncould never scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting correction!\N0-1-6, 0-1-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fire, fire, fire,\Nfire, fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The water, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see...\NThe soles of its feet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The water isn't being sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rear armor! Below and to the right of\Nthe intake! The gap between the claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We knew that your\Nbarrier had gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ground contact surfaces, for instance.\NYou can't put up a barrier under your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you did, you wouldn't\Nbe able to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The very invincibility of your\Nbarrier makes it impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to completely cover\Nyourself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The receiver for your external cameras.\NThat's one of the barrier's gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Martian princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Trillram! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being sarcastic?!\NWhere have you been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been making temporary repairs\Nto the sky carrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to it! We're leaving\Nthis place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, wait! Princess Asseylum...\NShe is alive! I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to kill her\Nand make certain this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How big a fool are you,\Nyou inferior scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I let her live, my entire clan and its\Nfollowers will be branded as traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, what do you\Nthink you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me tha-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That parade, it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were the ones who tried\Nto assassinate the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll... regret this...
